    # BarCamp Rochester
    ## Rochester's Geek Unconference

    BarCamp Rochester is an ad-hoc gathering born from the desire for people to share and learn in an open environment. BarCamp Rochester is an intense event with discussions, demos, and interaction from attendees. All attendees should give a demo, a session, or help with one. All presentations are scheduled the day they happen. Prepare in advance, but come early to get a good slot on the schedule.

    Check-in begins around 8:00AM, with the first presentations starting at 9:00AM.

    ### BarCamp / CloudCamp Rochester, #{data.global.next_event}

    BarCamp Rochester will be co-hosted with CloudCamp Rochester and held at the Rochester Institute of Technology on **#{data.global.next_date}**.
    This is the same unconference style day of fun and learning as always.

    If you want to learn more about how BarCamp Rochester works, you can always check out [our How-To page](/howto/).

